extends layouts/default

-title = 'sugarPhlox.'

block content

  header
    img(src='public/img/sugarPhlox.png')

  .row.hey-hey-know-me#about
    .container-fluid
      .col-xs-12.col-sm-5
        img.img-circle(
          src='public/img/itsame-mario.png'
        )
      .col-xs-12.col-sm-7
        h1 About Me
        p
          | Born in Massachusetts, I grew up surrounded with love and support by my family to
          | pursue anything I enjoyed in the world, and took full advantage of that. In high school
          | I enjoyed finer arts and photography, and took that with me to Salem State University
          | (based in Salem, MA), where I received my degree in Graphic Design (after starting as
          | a Biology major... really).
        p
          | In summer 2013, I looked at my cat Buddy and said 'We're moving to Burlington, VT', and
          | a month later I moved, and soon after started learning front end development, which 
          | has brought me here today.
        p
          | Other than my love for various forms of art, I do enjoy a good life in VT. My passions
          | include my vehicles (a 2009 Subaru WRX and a motorcycle), good cooking, my fantastic cat,
          | and learning something new every day.
  .row.portfolio#portfolio
    .container-fluid
      .col-xs-12.text-center
        h1 Portfolio
        .col-sm-6.col-sm-offset-3
          p
            | My work has a wide range covering different interests and fields. This includes
            | graphic design, front end development, photography, print making, and more.
